  "body": "When  ethereum node run in dev mode, if the block number increase to a big muber blocks,maybe 1 millions block, then use ethclient to call getBlock function,the header unmarshal will be error.\r\n\r\nI investigated it,the reason is that the difficult is not make change for dev mode ethereum node\r\n\r\nThe code maybe changed as following in the concensus.go file,in the function Prepare:\r\n\r\nfunc (ethash *Ethash) Prepare(chain consensus.ChainReader, header *types.Header) error {\r\n   ..\r\n\tif ethash.config.PowMode == ModeFake || ethash.config.PowMode == ModeFullFake {\r\n\t\theader.Difficulty = new(big.Int).SetUint64(1)\r\n\t} else {\r\n\t\theader.Difficulty = ethash.CalcDifficulty(chain, header.Time.Uint64(), parent)\r\n\t}\r\n\r\n}\r\n",
